<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ã‘ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§é…å»¶æ™‚é–“\(t'\)ã¨é€šå¸¸ã®æ™‚é–“\(t\)ã¨ã®é–“ã«\(t' = t - R(t')/c, dt = \kappa dt'\)ã®é–¢ä¿‚ãŒã‚ã‚‹ãŸã‚ã€(12)å¼ã®ç©åˆ†ã¯</p>

\[\hat{\mathbf{E}} (\omega) 
= \frac{q}{2\pi c} \int_{-\infty}^\infty \left[ \frac{\mathbf{n} \times \{ (\mathbf{n}(t') - \boldsymbol{\beta} (t')) \times \dot{\boldsymbol{\beta}} (t')\}}{\kappa^2(t') R(t')}\right] e^{i\omega (t' + R(t') / c)} dt' \tag{13}\]

